des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your home devices. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “Soleus Home Comfort” app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our “Soleus Home Comfort” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search “Home Comfort” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable “Home Comfort” skill, and you'll be navigated to “Home Comfort” login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, Turn on the Air purifier
Alexa, Turn off the Air purifier
Alexa, Change the mode to auto on the Air purifier
Alexa, Change the mode to manual on the Air purifier
